Distance of data points from the nearest plate boundary in degree

Usage

distance_from_pb(x, ep, pb, tangential = FALSE)

Arguments

x, pb

sf objects of the data points and the plate boundary geometries in the geographical coordinate system

ep

data.frame of the geographical coordinates of the Euler pole (lat, lon)

tangential

Logical. TRUE for tangential boundaries and FALSE (the default) for inward and outward boundaries.

Value

Numeric vector of the (great circle) distances in degree
